### Example 3: Transaction Entity

For entity "Orders" with fields: ID (UUID), OrderNumber (TEXT, MaxLength: 50, Unique), CustomerID (UUID, FK → Customers), OrderDate (datetime), TotalAmount (decimal), Status (TEXT, ValueList), ShipDate (datetime), Notes (TEXT, MaxLength: MAX)

